title: Statement by NSC Spokesperson Emily Horne on National Security Advisor Jake Sullivanâ€™s Meeting with National Security Advisor Moeed Yusuf of Pakistan | The White House
content: The National Security Advisors of the United States and Pakistan met in Geneva yesterday. Both sides discussed a range of bilateral, regional, and global issues of mutual interest and discussed ways to advance practical cooperation. Both sides agreed to continue to the conversation.###
